74 cosmetic preparations, with or without massage, on the scalp,
75 face, arms, legs, feet, or hands, esthetics practices, nail
76 technology, manicure, pedicure, or desairology.
77 (8) ESTHETICIAN. Any person, other than a student or
78 apprentice, who performs esthetics on the general public for
